Package: lossdb
Type: Package
Title: Automate common tasks involving insurance loss data sets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2014-04-14
Author: Andy Merlino
Maintainer: Andy Merlino <merlinoa88@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a standardized S3 object for storing insurance loss data.
    Additionally provides functions for many frequenctly used manipulations, 
    visualizations, and summaries of insurance loss data sets.
License: GPL-3
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: yes
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
